header.gameNote: BIG WEST CONFERENCE MEN'S TOURNAMENT - SEMIFINAL

videos.description: With the game tied in the final seconds of overtime, Chima Moneke grabs an offensive rebound and scores on the putback to give UC Davis a 66-64 win over CS Fullerton in a semifinal matchup of the Big West tournament.
videos.headline: UC Davis bests CS Fullerton at the buzzer
